column1: Daily Weather Observations for Willow Grove, Victoria for March 2016
Prepared at 13:04 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW3100.201603
Willow Grove does not take observations every day. Consequently, some of the rainfall and evaporation readings are of totals accumulated over several days.
Observations were drawn from Willow Grove (Blue Rock Reservoir) {station 085283}
